OL,6,FA father-of-three has been jailed for
OL,7,Fcalling for mosques to be burned down
OL,8,Fin Facebook posts.
OL,10,FGeraint Boyce, 43, has been jailed for
OL,11,Ftwo years after pleading guilty to
OL,12,Fpublishing threatening material
OL,13,Fintending to stir up religious hatred.
OL,15,FBoyce, from Tonypandy in Rhondda Cynon
OL,16,FTaf, was sentenced at Merthyr Tydfil
OL,17,FCrown Court on Thursday, 10 October,
OL,18,Fover Facebook posts published during
OL,19,Fthe riots earlier this year.
