OL,3,CDad jailed after calling for mosques
OL,4,Cto be burned down in Facebook posts
OL,6,FThe defendant made and shared a series
OL,7,Fof comments on 31 July including ones
OL,8,Fwhich called for mosques to be burned
OL,9,Fdown.
OL,11,FAlex Orndal, prosecuting, told the
OL,12,Fcourt the posts had been made
OL,13,Ffollowing the murder of three children
OL,14,Fat a Taylor Swift-themed dance class
OL,15,Fin Southport and the widespread
OL,16,Fdisruption that followed.
