OL,3,CDad jailed after calling for mosques
OL,4,Cto be burned down in Facebook posts
OL,6,FHe said the comments were made on a
OL,7,Fpublic Facebook profile called
OL,8,F"Boyce's Plumbing", which the
OL,9,Fdefendant had been logged into on
OL,10,Farrest.
OL,12,FOther posts included him saying he was
OL,13,F"ready for war" and "time to wake the
OL,14,Flion to save our children's future".
OL,16,FMr Orndal said he also shared an AI-
OL,17,Fgenerated picture of a "large hulk-
OL,18,Flike figure" chasing people wearing
OL,19,F"Islamic religious clothing".
