OL,3,CDad jailed after calling for mosques
OL,4,Cto be burned down in Facebook posts
OL,6,FOn arrest, Boyce asked police if it
OL,7,Fwas "because of the online stuff to do
OL,8,Fwith the riots".
OL,10,FMr Orndal said: "It is the Crown's
OL,11,Fcase that these are not mere idle
OL,12,Fcomments but calls to action."
OL,14,FNicholas Gedge, appearing for the
OL,15,Fdefence, insisted Boyce was "ashamed
OL,16,Fof what he did" and that he "wants
OL,17,Fpeople to live peacefully together".
OL,19,F"He held views at the time as a result
OL,20,Fof what he had seen online,
OL,21,Funfortunately," he said.
