OL,6,F"He was sympathetic to views that were
OL,7,Fwrong, which he wholly recognises now."
OL,9,FSentencing, Judge Tracey Lloyd-Clarke,
OL,10,Fthe Recorder of Cardiff, said: "A
OL,11,Fpolice officer viewed your account and
OL,12,Fsaw that you had posted threatening
OL,13,Fmaterial intended to stir up religious
OL,14,Fhatred."
OL,16,FShe said the posts showed an intention
OL,17,Fto "incite serious violence".
